Task
Maximum and minimum value in an array
Write a function maxMin that takes the arr array as arguments and returns an array containing the maximum and minimum value: [max, min]. If the array is empty, return [].
Example:
• function maxMin ([3, 4, 8, 1]) must return [8, 1];
• function maxMin ([7, 7]) must return [7, 7];
• function maxMin ([2]) must return [2, 2];
• function maxMin ([]) must return [];

Solution
function maxMin(arr){
 let max = Math.max(...arr);
  let min = Math.min(...arr);
  if(arr.length === 0) return [];
  return [max, min];
}
